            	<div class="description color-black  body-text"><p>Built with over 80 billion transistors using a cutting edge TSMC 4N process, Hopper features five groundbreaking innovations that fuel the <a href="/data-center/h200/">NVIDIA H200</a> and <a href="/data-center/h100/">H100 Tensor Core GPUs</a> and combine to deliver incredible speedups over the prior generation on generative AI training and inference.</p></div>
            
